    "keywords": "Revision of a revision, Concurrent revisionary jurisdiction, Permissive approach and Restrictive approach, Article 138 of the Constitution, Section 9 of the Act No. 19 of 1990.",
    "legistation": "The Primary Court\u2019s Procedure Act, No. 44 of 1979, The High Court of the Provinces (Special Provisions) Act No. 19 of 1990",
