    "md5": "e72b65b093f0ca932663cd7a37ee2ff9",
    "chunk_size_bytes": 619,
    "chunk_text": "when assessing the reliability of the appellant\u2019s testimony. The failure to challenge the prosecution witnesses on this crucial point undermines the appellant\u2019s position and makes it difficult to support the claim that the payment in question was unrelated to the matters at hand. Given this context, the\n\nPage 7 of 7\n\nlearned High Court Judge\u2019s decision to disregard the appellant\u2019s testimony is well founded.\n\n23. Due to the matters discussed above, I am not inclined to interfere with the\n\nof Colombo for compliance.\n\nJudge of the Court of Appeal\n\nB. SASI MAHENDRAN, J.\n\nI agree\n\nJudge of the Court of Appeal"
