adre approval. In these\n\ncircumstances, the petitioners certainly will have the expectation of\n\nbeing attached and absorbed to the Department of Archaeology without\n\nany other interview or examination. However, by 4R-4 and 4R-5, there\n\nappears to have been a change that such persons may be required to\n\nface an interview. It is in view of this change of policy and procedure that\n\nthe petitioners have applied and faced the interviews in 2019.\n\n27. Up until such time, all the petitioners did have a legitimate expectation\n\nof being absorbed to the Department of Archaeology. However, the"
