mara for the\n\nPetitioner.\n\n4\n\nDilantha Sampath, S.C. for the Respondents.\n\nArgued on: 06.11.2025\n\nDelivered on: 19.12.2025\n\nDr. D. F. H. Gunawardhana, J."
